# Keep the Docker build context small. The Dockerfile only needs:
#   - auth/pom.xml + auth/src/  (to build the JAR)
#   - ca-cert/cert.pem          (optional, for corporate MITM)
#
# Everything else under hapi/ (igs/, application.yaml, etc.) is mounted
# into the container at runtime by docker-compose, not baked into the
# image.

igs/
application.yaml
README.md
auth/target/
auth/.idea/
auth/*.iml
